of theyr dyewty of cle<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">e &amp; holy mynistra+cyon
&amp; lyuynge / &amp; haue set fur<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">h &amp; vsed
all vnlawfull tradycyons &amp; vayne lu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">|uryous
werk&abis; of ba<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">dry and for<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> cac<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">|on
/ I may not wryt so large w^t my <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 word">
as I culde / onely for to vtter to moche
